p;</font></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 66, 154);">10 000 points de marque,&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 66, 154);">3000 points de trace et 100 routes avec 30 points chacune.</span></div><div align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#00429a">Bouton MOB (Man over board).</font></span></div><div align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#00429a">Alarmes : Arrivée, Sécurité d''ancrage, XTE, Vitesse, SBAS, Parcours, Odomètre.</font></span></div><div align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><font color="#00429a">Démarrage à froid : 32 secondes.</font></span></div><span style="text-align: right; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 66, 154);"><div align="left" style="text-align: left;"><br></div></span><span style="text-align: right;"></span><div align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 66, 154);">Alimentation : 12/24 Volts - 0,24/0,12 Amp, avec protection de surintensité.</span></div><span style="text-align: right; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 66, 154);"><div align="left" style="text-align: left;"><br></div></span><span style="text-align: right;"></span><div align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 66, 154);">Mesures : 181(L) * 143(H) * 83(P) mm</span></div><div align="left"><br></div><div align="left"><font color="#00429a"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Expédition rapide, en recommandé contre signature.</span></font></div><strong style="text-align: right; line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-size: x-large; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div align="left" style="text-align: left;"><br><img border="0" src="http://www.huayang-tech.com/upload/editorfiles/2013.8.20_18.54.49_1330.jpg" style="border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br><img border="0" src="http://www.huayang-tech.com/upload/editorfiles/2013.8.20_18.55.11_3373.jpg" style="border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br><img border="0" src="http://www.huayang-tec